242
00:14:06,044 --> 00:14:09,734
None of these exist locally
designed for them from the start.

243
00:14:10,424 --> 00:14:12,674
And governance is a first class concern.

244
00:14:12,944 --> 00:14:17,954
Once the agent touch production or
put validation, human in the loop.

245
00:14:17,954 --> 00:14:21,194
Escalation and audit
logging are non-negotiable.

246
00:14:21,694 --> 00:14:22,384
Three tensions.

247
00:14:22,384 --> 00:14:24,724
He will always have to navigate.

248
00:14:25,159 --> 00:14:29,689
Latency versus accuracy,
autonomy versus auditability,

249
00:14:30,199 --> 00:14:31,999
generality versus reliability.

250
00:14:32,509 --> 00:14:37,519
You just get better at calibrating them,
build the systems that you can trust.

251
00:14:38,019 --> 00:14:41,844
Thank you so much for listening in,
and I'm happy to take any questions.

